snippet.title: DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince is coming to Nintendo Switch on December 1, 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/dragon-quest-monsters-the-dark-prince-switch/

DRAGON QUEST MONSTERS: The Dark Prince follows Psaro and his companion Rose as they travel through the demon realm of Nadiria. Explore and scout monsters onto your team, freely combine raised monsters to create more powerful allies, and take on enemies with your powerful team.

#dqmonsters #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
